data.description: Need more space??? The Timberland plan on a full unfinished basement has everything you're lookin for in a new home. With 4 bedrooms, 3 full baths and a large finished bonus area on the upper level... there is plenty of room for everyone. This home is beautifully finished with Quartz countertops in the Kitchen and Baths, Stainless Steel Appliances, Mohawk RevWood Flooring in Kitchen, Dining Room, Breakfast Area and Family Room. Custom Tile in Master Bath including Fully Tiled Shower, Tub Surround and Floor. Exterior is Low-Maintenance Concrete Siding, with a large rear deck. High efficiency zoned HVAC system. Full Unfinished basement provides a lot of room for expansion or... tons of storage space. Situated on wooded 5.0 Acre lot only minutes from Downtown Tallapoosa!
